{"tid":542582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"獨生細個好似得到所有資源 但係","createTime":"2018-01-27T15:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T02:18:19.000Z","uid":27741,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e47bc5503d97ca26cf70f73d06b352f0438cfd69","tid":542582,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"到父母退休 成頭家要孭上身 <br />\n（你老豆大把留俾你另計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n如果兩老多病更大負擔<br />\n但係又唔可以一走了之<br />\n兩老仆心仆命養大你 錫你 俾曬最好嘅你 <br />\n（唔計啲放置型家長）<br />\n我做唔出<br />\n但係有時喺度諗 <br />\n我到時係咪真係養得起個家<br />\n我一個人 係咪真係承擔到咁多野<br />\n衣食住行醫療 每個月洗費幾咁大<br />\n我fg屋企人就退休了<br />\n到時點樣生活"},{"pid":"9c178f9685932c6130dfa6d71908d963afd6885a","tid":542582,"uid":27741,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"即使佢地有些少積蓄 都唔搣得幾耐<br />\n仲有 我都想日後建立一個自己嘅新家庭<br />\n但係我怕我連自己生活都搞唔掂<br />\n種無力感大到"},{"pid":"ae27e54e44effbd2b949a8bea6b2a0a556584658","tid":542582,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"啊啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"b5350949a664f11490f088e2ebbf38d55048721d","tid":542582,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae27e54e44effbd2b949a8bea6b2a0a556584658","tid":542582,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"啊啊啊啊啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496475d048cfd1b6e3a62e51eefe2386e59fb933","tid":542582,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5350949a664f11490f088e2ebbf38d55048721d","tid":542582,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae27e54e44effbd2b949a8bea6b2a0a556584658","tid":542582,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"啊啊啊啊啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" 